Text: Construction Expedition Letter Cc Here is my attempt at modifying the letter to conform to our discussions this afternoon The redline markings indicate changes to a clean version of the draft sent yesterday This draft incorporates a slightly modified version of the confidentiality statement you provided earlier today changed Parties to Party etc Please acknowledge receipt GulfExpediteLetterdoc

FPSC Docket No EU Cc FYI The attached order on the territorial dispute was issued The time frame for WFEC to file a motion for reconsideration of Order No PSCFOFEU with the FPSC expires on Monday January days from the date of the order is Saturday January therefore the time for filing is extended until the next business day If a motion for reconsideration is filed we have days in which to serve a response The time period for pursuing an appeal to the Florida Supreme Court is tolled until the FPSC disposes of any motion for reconsideration If no motion for reconsideration is filed then the time frame for filing a notice of appeal to the Florida Supreme Court expires Tuesday January days from the date of the order is Sunday January and Monday January is a holiday therefore the time for filing a notice of appeal is extended until the next business day
